videos.headline: UCLA's Lake picks off Slovis on USC's opening drive
videos.description: Kedon Slovis throws an interception directly to Quentin Lake to give the Bruins the ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA's Lake picks off Slovis on USC's opening drive) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: UCLA catches USC's defense off guard to score 33-yard TD
videos.description: UCLA snaps the ball quickly before the Trojans' defense can get into place and Ethan Fernea catches the short pass from Dorian Thompson-Robinson and takes it the rest of the way for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA catches USC's defense off guard to score 33-yard TD) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: Felton breaks tackle for UCLA TD
videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson passes the ball to Demetric Felton who evades a USC defender en route to a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Felton breaks tackle for UCLA TD) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: Even Chip Kelly has to give props to this USC TD
videos.description: Drake London catches a pass from Kedon Slovis and avoids being brought down by several UCLA defenders to score a 65-yard Trojans touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Even Chip Kelly has to give props to this USC TD) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: USC's Pola-Mao dives to secure INT
videos.description: Isaiah Pola-Mao bats Dorian Thompson-Robinson's pass into the air and dives to grab it on the way down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USC's Pola-Mao dives to secure INT) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: Thompson-Robinson, Felton connect for 2nd time to pad UCLA's lead before halftime
videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson finds Demetric Felton for a 12-yard score to put UCLA up 21-10 at the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson-Robinson, Felton connect for 2nd time to pad UCLA's lead before halftime) 2020/12/12

videos.headline: Slovis slings five TDs to lead USC to comeback win over UCLA
videos.description: Kedon Slovis throws for 344 yards and five touchdowns as the Trojans come from behind to beat their crosstown rivals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Slovis slings 5 TDs to lead USC to comeback win over UCLA) 2020/12/12 ESHEET SOTFULL
